I see you've already met her.

130
00:12:51,688 --> 00:12:54,476
Hey, new passengers?

131
00:12:54,691 --> 00:12:56,227
That's just great.

132
00:12:56,985 --> 00:12:58,851
Please excuse me.

133
00:12:59,028 --> 00:13:03,113
I'm sure our Captain Ortega will be happy
to show you his ship.

134
00:13:04,367 --> 00:13:05,653
Captain.

135
00:13:06,828 --> 00:13:10,037
You must have come on board with the last group.

136
00:13:10,206 --> 00:13:12,198
I guess so. I'm Guzm√°n.

