216
00:19:01,807 --> 00:19:05,471
A glass of warm milk is all I need.

217
00:19:06,479 --> 00:19:07,686
I see.

218
00:19:08,439 --> 00:19:12,023
Could I maybe get a glass of milk for the Lady?

219
00:19:13,527 --> 00:19:16,520
